                     <interp inst="t18270913-129-person1337" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to the prosecutor and saw the prisoner take a six feet deal, out about eleven o'clock in the morning; and in the evening I saw him crossing the bridge with another.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-129-person1338">
