                     <interp inst="t18270913-129-person1339" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I went to the prosecutor's yard, and found an opening, through which a deal appeared to have been drawn.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I took none but what I was sent with by Mr. Cheeswright.</p>
